Revision history for App-Workflow-Lint - Linter for GitHub Actions workflow files

0.02
	[ Bug Fixes]

	- Fix: add missing fix_file() method to App::Workflow::Lint facade.
	- Fix: Engine::fix_file now loads the workflow once and runs rules against
	  that single copy, so fix closures operate on the same structure that is
	  returned to the caller.
	- Fix: bin/workflow-lint --write now works; fix_file stores the engine on
	  $self so save_workflow() is reachable.
	- Fix: malformed YAML no longer crashes with a raw stack trace; YAML.pm
	  wraps load_string in eval and croaks with a clean message.
	- Fix: Rule dispatcher no longer dies on jobs: [] or steps: "scalar";
	  added ref-type guards before iterating jobs and steps.
	- Fix: MissingPermissions now uses check_workflow() and $self->diag()
	  instead of overriding check() and hand-rolling an incomplete hashref.
	- Fix: Formatter::_format_human returns empty string (not "\n") when
	  there are no diagnostics.
	- Fix: UnpinnedActions unsafe-tag regex is now case-insensitive (/i),
	  catching @Master, @MAIN, etc.

0.01	Wed Mar 18 08:42:06 EDT 2026
	- Initial release skeleton.
	- Basic engine, rule system, CLI, and first rule.
